        "can_view_edit_history": true,
        "can_wiki": false,
        "cooked": "<p>I had struggle with this same problem in some of my designs, and the way I \u201csolved\u201d it, was just adding a combo for selecting what part of the model you want to generate.<br>\nIn my opinion, or at least for the kind of projects I usually work on, the perfect solution would be to allow send parts of the project to different plates and export all of them at the same time</p>",
